name: hiMAYC
description: What is HIMAYC? hiMAYC is an ERC-20 token representing 1/1,000,000 ownership of a MAYC in the Meta-Swap pool of Fracton Protocol. About Otherdeed for Otherside: Otherdeed for Otherside is a collection of land plot NFTs for the Yuga Labs metaverse on the Ethereum blockchain. Each Otherdeed NFT grants holders the ability to claim Otherside land upon full Otherside launch. Each Otherdeed represents different environments and sediments within the Otherside.
